summary: Introducing Corgi Inu – the meme coin with royal charm! - Step into the world of Corgi Inu, the meme coin that’s not just adorable but also carries a royal pedigree. Loyal companion of Kabosu and the breed that stole Queen Elizabeth II’s heart (she had 25 Corgis!), Corgi Inu is here to bring you the best of both worlds—fun and financial potential.
